{"tid":1369681,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"防火知識：壓縮氣體遇火會引起火災或爆作","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T19:35:55.000Z","uid":234,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9a030945f81bd3924f69198a7d9d8c0d73b803","tid":1369681,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:16:13.000Z","msg":"今日想同大家分享一下平時身邊成日用個啲止汗劑呀噴髮膠<br />\n雖然合法買到但其實如果唔小心處理會好容易引起火災架<br />\n例如氣體接觸到火機噴出黎既火就會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變左火槍</span></span>咁真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好危險</span></span><br />\n呢啲野真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以綁埋一齊</span></span>好危險架<br />\n特別係打開個啲一開就長著既火機<br />\n萬一佢地痴埋左一齊要小心處理唔好整親埋自己<br />\n更加唔可以直接掉落火堆會大爆炸架！<br />\n所以易燃危險品記住一定要同火同熱力隔絕呀<br />\n祝大家出入平安 香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27055bf3118e65ccc83926ecfe3c1f0afa10465","tid":1369681,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:18:08.000Z","msg":"防火知識 人人要識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4914c55c13b699c54e88d3fcbdaea945eb3db89e","tid":1369681,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:22:49.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"909b3c1e3e701b34930ca5c982c945a770b81f98","tid":1369681,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:25:07.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ece144d0103cb4de6ed5363322cea3b604715b28","tid":1369681,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:25:18.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4032d4f46b9a80a9daff428b74dc47c3826c9dd6","tid":1369681,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:26:47.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"567a09de5edf805a2e64bb445c7d5434310ad740","tid":1369681,"uid":97840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"元朗好多野食，隨時有好多